1UY.F.summary: Atal S.A. develops and sells residential building complexes in Poland. The company develops housing estates, and single and multi-family houses. It operates in Gliwice, Katowice, Cracow, Lodz, Wroclaw, Warsaw, Tricity, and Poznan. The company was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Cieszyn, Poland. Atal S.A. is a subsidiary of Juroszek Investments Sp. z o.o.
